   "source": [
    "Teleportation is restricted to two nodes with median PageRank values. After doing this, the results change a lot. These two nodes receive much higher visit probabilities than before, because the walker keeps returning to them through teleportation. At the same time, the overall ranking becomes strongly influenced by these two nodes. This shows that personalized teleportation can significantly change PageRank and make it depend heavily on user preference."
